                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Hours (confirm before visit): Mon, Tue, Thu & Fri 3:00 PM–11:00 PM; Sat, Sun, Malaysian school holidays & public holidays 12:00 PM–12:00 AM. Closed Wednesdays except on public holidays and school holidays. CMS also lists Sat–Sun 10 AM–10 PM and Mon/Tue/Thu/Fri 2 PM–10 PM—verify on Gamuda Land / FunPark channels."
